                  <Label style="-fx-font-size: 16; -fx-font-weight: bold;" text="📘 Theoretical Explanation" />
                  <TextFlow layoutX="-2.0" layoutY="3.0" prefHeight="92.0" prefWidth="574.0" textAlignment="CENTER">
                     <Text style="-fx-font-size: 14;" text="When two or more vectors are added their resultant vector is formed. The sum of x component of all the vectors will be equal to that of the resultant vector. The y component of the resultant will be equal to the sum of all y components of the vectors." wrappingWidth="520" />
