                  <Label prefHeight="86.0" prefWidth="574.0" style="-fx-font-size: 14;" text="Suppose there are n vectors of equal magnitude. If they maintain same angle between adjacent vectors, at what angle will the resultant be null vector?" wrapText="true" />

